**Final Conclusion:**  
The application exhibits multiple behaviors consistent with malware, including excessive permissions, potential data leakage, and insecure handling of web content. Given these indicators, it is recommended to treat this application as malicious and to implement measures to block its installation and usage. Further investigation and monitoring are advised to mitigate potential risks to user privacy and security.